{"tid":1913787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世衛：無證據顯示武肺病毒會於夏季消失","createTime":"2020-03-07T05:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T05:39:13.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b40797bf88d6361235d938e95cf2d9b511ac5e","tid":1913787,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200307/s00005/f901ff40b9baae57c312ed0c26875e92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200307%2Fs00005%2Ff901ff40b9baae57c312ed0c26875e92.jpg&h=0675ae81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世衛公共衛生緊急項目負責人瑞安（Michael Ryan）周五（6日）表示，世界各國領導人不要以為新型冠狀病毒會像流感般在夏季消失，應假設病毒繼續具傳播力。世衛總幹事譚德塞則呼籲，各國應繼續將遏制疫情放在首位。<br />\n<br />\n瑞安表示，暫不清楚病毒在不同氣候情況下的活躍程度，因此要假設病毒仍會繼續具傳播力。他說：「這是一個錯誤的希望，若說它在夏季會如流感般消失，我們不能做這個假設，這並無證據。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200307/s00005/1583542802194/【新冠肺炎】世衛-無證據顯示新冠病毒會於夏季消失\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200307%2Fs00005%2F1583542802194%2F%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B-%E7%84%A1%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%9C%83%E6%96%BC%E5%A4%8F%E5%AD%A3%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnKjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=b382cf7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200307%2Fs00005%2F1583542802194%2F%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B-%E7%84%A1%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%9C%83%E6%96%BC%E5%A4%8F%E5%AD%A3%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1&h=374721d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200307/s00005/1583542802194/【新冠肺炎】世衛-無證據顯示新冠病毒會於夏季消失</a>"},{"pid":"8fc09823f39cc0c4eb66986acef70fa9b1caeda4","tid":1913787,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep